casebody.data:
No. 276,

Misc.

Knetzer v. Schultz, Acting U. S. Marshal. Donald H. Dalton and Manuel M. Wiseman for petitioner.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied.

Mr. Justice Black, Mr. Justice Reed, and Mr. Justice Douglas are of the opinion that the application should be transferred under 28 U. S. C. § 2241 (b).
